sec.p:
Mouse mDia2 cDNA (mKIAA4117) was obtained from Kazusa DNA Research Institute. Mouse mDia3 cDNA fragments were cloned from mouse brain mRNA by RT-PCR using Omniscript Reverse Transcriptase and ProofStart DNA Polymerase (Qiagen, Valencia, CA). Three primer sets used were:
5´-AGAGAAAGATGGAGGAGCTCG-3´ and 5´-AGTTCAGCTGCAGCAGTGATG-3´;
5´-CTGCTATTTGCATTGTTGGGG-3´ and 5´-GAAGGAAATGTCAAGGCCAGT-3´;
5´-GGTCCAAGATTGAGCCTAAAG-3´ and 5´-CTTAAATGTCTCCATTCTCCC-3´.

siRNA-resistant (r) RhoD, mDia1, mDia2, mDia3A, mDia3B, and mDia3C cDNAs were constructed by introducing point mutations into wild-type cDNAs by PCR. The primer sets used were:
siRNA(2)-r RhoD: 5´-GTTACAACGCCACTCTGCAGATGAAGG-3´ and 5´-GCTCGAACACTGTGGGACTGTAGCTCTC-3´;
siRNA(1)-r mDia1: 5´-CTTCCTGTGCAAGCTTCGAGACACCAAG­TC-3´ and 5´-GAGATATTGAAGCCGAAAGCACCAGCATTC-3´;
siRNA(1)-r mDia2: 5´-CAGAACCTTATAAAGCACCTTCCTGATGAG-3´ and 5´-GATCATTGACTCTGACAACTGTGTTTCATC-3´;
siRNA(1)-r mDia3A/B/C: 5´-CCGCGAACAGTATGACAAACTGTCCACC-3´ and 5´-GCGTTCTGTGTAAAGCTCATCATCTTTTCC-3´.

Mouse FGFR1c cDNA fragments were cloned from mRNA of mouse embryonic stem cell line R1 by RT-PCR. Two primers sets used were:
5´-ACGGATCCTTGTTACCAACCTCTAACCG-3´ and 5´-TGCCTAAGACCAGTCTGTCTCGTGGC-3´;
5´-TGGAGTCTCCGAATATGAGCTCCCTG-3´ and 5´-GGGGATCCGGCGCCGTTTGAGTCCACTG-3´.

Stealth RNAi siRNAs (Life Technologies) were used to knock down mouse RhoD and mDia1/2/3. The target sequences of the siRNAs were:
RhoD siRNA(1): 5´-CCAAACAGCTTTGACAACGTCTCCA-3´ (nt 374–398 from the initiation codon);
RhoD siRNA(2): 5´-CCCACAGTGTTTGAGCGCTATAATG-3´ (nt 142–166);
mDia1 siRNA(1): 5´-GCTTCAATATCAGCTTCCTTTGTAA-3´ (nt 2942–2966);
mDia1 siRNA(2): 5´-GGTTGATCAAATGATTGATAAAACA-3´ (nt 1365–1389);
mDia2 siRNA(1): 5´-CAGAGTCCATGATTCAGAACTTAAT-3´ (nt 2186–2210);
mDia2 siRNA(2): 5´-AGAAGATTGAATTGGTTAAAGATCG-3´ (nt 1876–1900);
mDia3 siRNA(1): 5´-GAGCTTTACCCAGAATGCCAGAGAA-3´ (nt 2868–2892);
mDia3 siRNA(2): 5´-GAAAGCATTTATGAATAATAAGTTT-3´ (nt 738–762);
negative control siRNA: 5´-GAGTTCACCGAAAGTCCGAATCGAA-3´.

The amounts RhoD and RhoF mRNAs were quantitated by real-time PCR. The cDNAs were synthesized from cytoplasmic RNA with SuperScript VILO cDNA Synthesis Kit (Life Technologies). The primer sets used were:
RhoD: 5´-GAAGACGTCACTGATGATGGTCTTCG-3´ and 5´-AAGCAGAGGAGCAAGACATTGGCATC-3´;
RhoF: 5´-AGTGTGACAGTGGGTAACAAGGAG-3´ and 5´-TGATGAGGACGTTGTCGTAACTGG-3´.
